T̈ö ïn̈s̈ẗäl̈l̈ ẗḧïs̈ m̈öd̈ül̈ë ẗÿp̈ë ẗḧë f̈öl̈l̈öẅïn̈g̈:̈

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

